"title": "5436: pain",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5436: pain",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A sense of physical suffering, anguish or distress, which has a number of causes. Scripture indicates the sources of pain and its potential spiritual implications and results.</p>\n<h2>Pain is universal</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:22\">ROM 8:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:16-Gen3:17\">GEN 3:16–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:7\">JOB 5:7</a></p>\n<h2>The origins of pain</h2>\n<h3>Satanic activity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:15\">GEN 3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:12\">JOB 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:6-Job2:7\">JOB 2:6–2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:16\">LUK 13:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:7\">2CO 12:7</a></p>\n<h3>Human activity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:14\">PSA 37:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:8\">GEN 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:10-Exod1:11\">EXO 1:10–1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:1-Nah3:4\">NAM 3:1–3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:6\">HAB 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:8\">HAB 2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:10\">HAB 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:12\">HAB 2:12</a></p>\n<h3>God's judgment and glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:2-John9:3\">JHN 9:2–9:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:11\">EXO 9:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:10-Num12:11\">NUM 12:10–12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:19-2Chr26:20\">2CH 26:19–26:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:3-Ps38:5\">PSA 38:3–38:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:11\">PRO 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:23\">ACT 12:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:11\">ACT 13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:9\">2CO 12:9</a></p>\n<h2>Kinds of pain</h2>\n<h3>Physical pain</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:7\">PSA 38:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:17\">JOB 30:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:28\">MAT 10:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:33\">LUK 23:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:16-2Cor4:18\">2CO 4:16–4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:23-2Cor11:27\">2CO 11:23–11:27</a></p>\n<h3>Mental pain</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:18\">JER 15:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:5-Ps42:6\">PSA 42:5–42:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:11\">PSA 42:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:6\">JER 12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:38\">MAT 26:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:13\">2CO 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:8\">2PE 2:8</a></p>\n<h3>Bereavement</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:33-John11:35\">JHN 11:33–11:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:18\">GEN 35:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:1\">GEN 50:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:22-2Sam12:23\">2SA 12:22–12:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:27\">PHP 2:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:13\">1TH 4:13</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual pain</h2>\n<h3>Conviction of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:8\">JHN 16:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:3-Ps32:5\">PSA 32:3–32:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:1-Ps51:2\">PSA 51:1–51:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:38\">LUK 7:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:14\">ACT 26:14</a></p>\n<h3>The anguish of hell</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:47-Mark9:48\">MRK 9:47–9:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:22\">MAT 5:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:12\">MAT 8:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:28\">LUK 13:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:16\">REV 6:16</a></p>\n<h3>Perplexity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:10\">ISA 50:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:8-Job23:9\">JOB 23:8–23:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:1\">PSA 22:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps88:1-Ps88:3\">PSA 88:1–88:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:7\">JER 20:7</a></p>\n<h3>Concern for others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:19\">GAL 4:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:19\">ACT 20:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:1-2Cor2:5\">2CO 2:1–2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:28\">2CO 11:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:18\">PHP 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:28-Col2:1\">COL 1:28–2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:7\">HEB 5:7</a></p>\n<h3>The failure of others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:56\">MAT 26:56</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:40\">MAT 26:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:21\">JHN 13:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:16\">GAL 4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:10\">2TI 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:16\">2TI 4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:10\">3JN 1:10</a></p>\n<h2>Fruitful results of pain</h2>\n<h3>It draws believers to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:19\">1PE 4:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:1\">JHN 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:18\">JHN 14:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:26\">ROM 8:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:5-2Cor7:6\">2CO 7:5–7:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:15-Heb4:16\">HEB 4:15–4:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:8\">HEB 5:8</a></p>\n<h3>It equips believers to help others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:4\">2CO 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:3-Rom5:5\">ROM 5:3–5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:15\">ROM 12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:18\">HEB 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:11\">HEB 12:11</a></p>\n<h3>It helps believers to anticipate the resurrection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:54-1Cor15:57\">1CO 15:54–15:57</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:19\">ROM 8:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:17\">2CO 4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:14\">1TH 4:14</a></p>\n<h3>It points believers to heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:4\">REV 21:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:18\">ROM 8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:15-Rev7:17\">REV 7:15–7:17</a></p>",
